=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Classes_UGen_ex4 ===

DESCRIPTION: A very_dark pure_tone sound, with complex oscillator character around 444 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally simple.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: very_dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: pure_tone
  spectral_complexity_mean: simple
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 443.8278
  harmonic_decay_rate: -15.4328
  harmonic_regularity: 0.5060
  pitch_clarity: 100.6996
  inharmonicity: 0.0264
  type: complex
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -4.8558
  resonance_freq: 452.1973

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
// Title: UGen Example 4
// Author: SC Documentation
// URL: http://doc.sccode.org/Classes/UGen.html
// Tags: UGen, Classes
// ---
// --- Example 4 ---
{ SinOsc.ar(LFNoise0.ar(2).range(420, 460).poll(label: \LFNoise), 0, 0.2) }.play;

// multichannel polling:
(
{
    var freqs = SinOsc.ar([0.2, 0.3]).range(420, 460);
    freqs.poll(label: [\freq1, \freq2]);
    SinOsc.ar(freqs, 0, 0.2);
}.play;
)
